<%= render_overridable "items", "search_preset_header" %>

<p>This digital edition of the correspondence of Charles W. Chesnutt offers hundreds of letters, incoming and outgoing, as well as drafts, dating from 1883 to 1932. With letters relating to personal, political, business, civic, and literary matters, the edition illuminates the expansive social and literary network of this prominent African American writer, lawyer, and voting rights activist and sheds light on his times. The edition includes transcriptions along with images of the original documents whenever possible. Our editorial policies can be found <%= link_to "here", about_editorial_policy_path %>.</p>

<br/>

<h4><%= link_to "Full Introduction to the Correspondence of Chesnutt", correspondence_intro_path %></h4>

<br/>

<h4><%= link_to "Complete Catalog of All Incoming and Outgoing Letters", correspondence_catalog_path %></h4>

  <br/>

